top_comment.text:
Today I was thinking of killing myself because I'm abused and bullied, then 
I saw your videos and I started watching them. I love your videos, you're 
amazing and talented and kind, and you always make me smile. You and Mamrie 
make me so happy and excited, I want to live longer. Thank you <3

Please no hate😔﻿
top_comment.author: Ana Victoria

comments.text:
+Ana Victoria msg me anytime- im going throught the same stuff you can tell 
me anything- just remember you need to tell an adult no matter how scared  
it is important you get help
comments.author: Sarah Roushdi

comments.text:
Girl all you gotta do is remember you always have a friend even if you 
don't know who that friend is someone out there is supporting you if 
someone cares about you they ARE your friend i care about you 😊😉
comments.author: Harlow Murawski

comments.text:
Hi i know how u feel but u should be always keep going and and always think 
about the good not the bad
comments.author: Cecilia Roldan

comments.text:
+Ana Victoria Stay strong, you're gorgeous don't let anyone tell you 
different. Don't ever put your life on the line because there are people 
that you know and even don't know that actually cared about you and if you 
left this world many hearts will be broken. Tyler has helped out a lot on 
these situations with The Trevor Project, no one should ever give you hate, 
in a matter of fact no one in this world should get hated on but society is 
society. Again, stay strong beautiful and remember there are people in your 
life who actually cares about you and don't want you to leave this world; 
God made you and put you in this world for a reason, for you to live.
comments.author: Bryona Schiller

comments.text:
Be strong !!! And trust that Tyler is always gonna be here for all of us, 
we're a family ! #TeamInternet
comments.author: Irina Ratcu

comments.text:
+Ana Victoria Honey you are amazing and i just wanted to say you are 
incredible and worth everything. Stay strong and remember that you are 
completely amazing and there is always a way out. I've been bullied as well 
and i know completely where you are coming from. I've been to that dark 
place where you feel worthless and insignificant, then i found some true 
friends and eventually everyone just pissed off because I and my friends 
stood up for me. Basically what i'm getting at is stay strong and do the 
things that make you happy. Youtube was my escape. I didn't have people 
like the others who replied when i went through this, which is why i will 
try to help anyone in this sort of situation. Tyler was my rock - he'll 
work for you too xxxxx
comments.author: Selena Mantikos

comments.text:
TYSM, you're all amazing and kind never stop :D you make me feel amazing 
and like I'm worth something thanks so much <3
comments.author: Ana Victoria

comments.text:
Stay strong I don't know you but I already love you 😜😭💯💯💯 your perfect 
don't let hate get you down ever ever ever please stay strong 😘😘💯💯💯💯
comments.author: Megarose Sorenson

comments.text:
+Ana Victoria Stay strong! Just so you know the people who abuse and bully 
you aren't half the person you are, if they need to resort to that to make 
themselves feel better. Don't listen to them, there are always people out 
there who can help :)
